    com.djrapitops.plugin.IPlugin, IPlan, org.bukkit.command.CommandExecutor, org.bukkit.command.TabCompleter, org.bukkit.command.TabExecutor, org.bukkit.plugin.Plugin 

    public class Plan
extends com.djrapitops.plugin.BukkitPlugin<Plan>
implements IPlan
    Main class for Bukkit that manages the plugin.

    Everything can be accessed through this class. Use Plan.getInstance() to get the initialised instance of Plan.

    1.0.0
